SCP-884-5 was the first of the objects to be completely understood by the Foundation. SCP-884-5 was a pair of silver scissors with an etched design (undescribed in existing documents) which were used to  things. Initial data noted in the personal records of the supervising doctor at the time recorded the basic effect:




